{"tid":1568380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我是藍絲，我有說話想說...","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T14:49:08.000Z","uid":55835,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac2d6a9202de8bb4edd74fcb6d878f0dbb4b099","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"（轉自身邊的一位嬸嬸，佢想我post係連登，因為佢唔識係好識字，所以我代佢打返大約意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我十多年前來香港定居，同老公生了2個女兒，一直心想自己唔使再點捱苦了，直到最近幾個月，甚至今日，我開始驚自己又要過返細過既困苦生活...... <br />\n<br />\n因為佔中 （按：佢指反送中），搞到啲酒樓無生意，我呢啲字都唔識多隻既，除咗洗碗仲可以做咩？ 但偏偏因為你哋班廢青，搞到我而家唔2係日日有工開中，只係靠住老公做小巴司機勉強生活.... <br />\n<br />\n我一直都問2得兩個女，點解要比人洗腦，人地收咗錢換你地既前途，點解你哋咁蠢接受？ 祖國有咩唔好？我舊時鄉下係生活難，但而家中國都起飛了啊？<br />\n<br />\n我一直相信中國香港人是有愛國的，所以兩三日前有朋友叫我一齊參與今日既愛國遊行，我問都無問就決定參加，因為我想話比我2個女知，愛祖國既人都無文明的，我們都等待香港人回來我們這邊。<br />\n<br />\n但係...  (按：呢位嬸嬸講到呢到有啲激動）<br />\n<br />\n點解身邊既人會係咁追打班後生？明明佢地都無搞過事，我試過叫停手，但有個男人同我講「呢班垃圾黎，打死唔使可憐啦」，個一刻我呆了，就連我叫人停止個時都比人扯埋一邊，叫我咪阻住做野......<br />\n<br />\n最後，我慢慢走向商場出口，找了一個地方坐下。<br />\n<br />\n我只係一個小女人，究竟我支持既係咩？ 點解愛國記就一定要打人？ 不是說青年人是我們未來嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦同我講咗一堆野，我唔識答佢，我應該點安慰佢好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fb98a997804449964c1d5847d65957309909a4","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0038157738acb6afd1fdb402126d097fa641d9d0","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"有無人土幫手解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79480c01fea30c9e895605724a503b0c531b89e6","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd337d055391d2bd8bcb1c381ae3cddb56410a08","tid":1568380,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"其他有良心藍絲都要知道嬸嬸既諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcab5e0689a794e3d902184cec8072658ea388b7","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd337d055391d2bd8bcb1c381ae3cddb56410a08","tid":1568380,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"其他有良心藍絲都要知道嬸嬸既諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:33:54.000Z","msg":"唔係話幫邊邊，但呢位嬸嬸係一個真正有血有肉既人，可以點幫佢好"},{"pid":"2e6793deb8f4546968e03fb686bcbbffadf28c6c","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:34:39.000Z","msg":"認真post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde2b7e782e02a52685911f8cbd4841fba3ed701","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b611870121e851ca9d2689efab332dd00e1ac34","tid":1568380,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:37:55.000Z","msg":"「就連我叫人停止個時都比人扯埋一邊，叫我咪阻住做野....」<br />\n阻膠阻人睇吓啦"},{"pid":"17785cf335037fce816f56a6106fda56db2641c0","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b611870121e851ca9d2689efab332dd00e1ac34","tid":1568380,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:37:55.000Z","msg":"「就連我叫人停止個時都比人扯埋一邊，叫我咪阻住做野....」<br />\n阻膠阻人睇吓啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:39:29.000Z","msg":"原來佢地都有左膠<br />\n<br />\n我都係第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bffc2a3606d76690c09c59a94668721bacc4a5","tid":1568380,"uid":276175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"呢個就係年青人命都唔要企出黎既目的，就係要中共同所謂既愛國謊言被揭穿！妳親眼目睹係有福既！"},{"pid":"43a582d4363c3e1cec47698eeedbf6d3bccf0068","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:43:37.000Z","msg":"佢有描述到現場個畫面<br />\n<br />\n話好亂，好多個男人衝上去，見後生就打<br />\n有個差啲打埋自己友"},{"pid":"5596e233b3c50769e5a9f0f53e39f0cac42419fb","tid":1568380,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a16c0b7389c279408582e302324b337cdec3db7","tid":1568380,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"震撼教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f3355de278a18984688e6343d69476dcc956a9","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"點算，無人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056a12a57ccaff7cf93ce68106c27de68a8a278e","tid":1568380,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55f3355de278a18984688e6343d69476dcc956a9","tid":1568380,"uid":55835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"點算，無人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"我睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6236234426a35628599c71c58ef03645c640144","tid":1568380,"uid":39375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face